cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use StructAI in your research or practice, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "StructAI: AI-Powered Civil Engineering Platform for Colombia"
abstract: >
  StructAI is a freemium SaaS platform that provides AI-assisted engineering
  calculations with full normative traceability for Colombian civil engineering
  standards (NSR-10, RAS 2000 / Res. 0330-2017, INVIAS, NTC, SGSST). It
  integrates six domain engines — unit price analysis (APU), structural
  mechanics, water and sanitation (AquAI), geotechnics (GeoPot), road design
  (Vías), and project management (Gerencia) — with a retrieval-augmented
  generation (RAG) pipeline that cites the exact norm, chapter, and article
  for every answer. The system uses local multilingual embeddings (sentence-
  transformers) stored in pgvector (Supabase/PostgreSQL) and Groq as the
  LLM synthesis backend.
